            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="11688232">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">上聞之慟曰：“天何不遺一人送朕老耶！”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-03-05 15:04</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                上聞之慟曰：“天何不遺一人送朕老耶！”
